    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>这款试玩版约有90分钟的游戏内容，将带你领略游戏的初步内容。</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款扣人心弦的平台冒险游戏中，你将于一片汇集古老寓言的广袤群岛展开旅程。请欣赏经典的手绘逐帧动画与美景，并打败一位神秘莫测的神灵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/e7a626869b6aabf3866bbeb90582f46f.avif?t=1772089479\" width=616 height=362 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/32bf891fd3a425c05b8b70b01417c040.poster.avif?t=1772089479\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/32bf891fd3a425c05b8b70b01417c040.webm?t=1772089479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/32bf891fd3a425c05b8b70b01417c040.mp4?t=1772089479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《戈德曼的永生》是一场别开生面却又充满黑暗的冒险之旅。游戏以与众不同的视角切入题材，传说、童话、神话在这里交织融合，故事中的每一次转折都会带给你出乎意料的体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你来到了群岛，肩负着一个奇怪的使命：杀死“神灵”：一个人人挂在嘴边，却又无人亲眼见过的神秘生物。为了寻找神灵，你要深入一座座岛屿，揭晓一个个秘密。你将踏入一个被悲剧所笼罩的世界，并在此遇见一群性情古怪的角色，切身体会强烈的反差感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过为手杖安装新组件和解锁新技能，你将能够探索群岛每一个隐秘的角落，并直面种种奇妙生物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/02daef1ed784702a310cb078d19c2599.avif?t=1772089479\" width=616 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/b9a4703333b1fe8ba1b06b33de0a6b54.poster.avif?t=1772089479\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/b9a4703333b1fe8ba1b06b33de0a6b54.webm?t=1772089479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/b9a4703333b1fe8ba1b06b33de0a6b54.mp4?t=1772089479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们与你一样，都欣赏并热爱着同样的动画、漫画和游戏，而《戈德曼的永生》便是我们数年心血的结晶。我们想打造一款臻于完美的 2D 游戏，并希望它能呈现惊艳无比的美感。所以我们追本溯源，采取了最艰难的方法——使用手工，逐帧绘制、上色和制作动画，一切力求完美。我们拒绝偷工减料，从最终结果看来，我们的努力结出了丰硕的果实。你不会在《The Eternal Life of Goldman》中发现相似的房间或景观。每处地点、每件物品、每位角色、每个视觉效果：一切都经过最精心的设计与编排。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还记得你在孩提时代初遇 16 位平台游戏的那一刻的震撼感吗？我们的目标就是带你重温那份惊喜——又或是帮你初次体验那种惊奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/4781b82c1bf21bb56c391605a5547331.avif?t=1772089479\" width=616 height=362 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/247c8dcc9970a238949354586eea0687.poster.avif?t=1772089479\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/247c8dcc9970a238949354586eea0687.webm?t=1772089479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4315490/extras/247c8dcc9970a238949354586eea0687.mp4?t=1772089479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《戈德曼的永生》绝非对陈词滥调的一味重复，而是选择了颠覆传统。我们在不同风格、潮流、年代的游戏中挑选大家最喜爱的横版游戏要素，并将其精心纳入这款游戏之中。同时，我们也剔除了所有毫无意义和浪费时间的恼人成分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款考验玩家精准操作的平台游戏，但绝不会变成倚赖死记和机械执行一连串特定动作的苦差事。要在游戏中实现成功，关键在于随机应变和突发奇想。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款鼓励探索并充满发现乐趣的游戏。但在这里，你不必每获得一个新技能或神器就要回过头再探索一遍老路。在这款游戏中，你绝不会在漫无目的的徘徊之中浪费时间，总有有趣的事物等你发现。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总而言之，这是一款场景丰富、人物立体、剧情深邃的游戏——但绝不会给你故作高深、无病呻吟之感。游戏内的所有元素浑然一体，构成了一段扣人心弦而又令人心碎的冒险之旅。</p>",
